00047 void DataSetTest_FStreamLoadEntireDataSet::setUp()
00048 {
00049         data = new GenericData;
00050         GenericFileReader reader;
00051         std::string name = TEST_DATA_DAT_FILE;
00052         reader.SetFilename(name);
00053         reader.ReadHeader(*data);
00054         DataGroupHdrIt dchBegin, dchEnd;
00055         data->Header().GetDataGroupIts(dchBegin, dchEnd);
00056         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dchBegin != dchEnd);
00057         DataSetHdrIt dphBegin, dphEnd;
00058         dchBegin->GetDataSetIterators(dphBegin, dphEnd);
00059         ifs.open(name.c_str(), std::ios::in | std::ios::binary);
00060         dataPlane = new DataSet(data->Header().GetFilename(), *dphBegin, ifs, true);
00061 }

00197 void DataSetTest_FStreamLoadEntireDataSet::testmethod_ReadUInt16_Vector_InChunks()
00198 {

00200 
00201         int32_t rows = dataPlane->Rows();
00202         int32_t chunks = 7;
00203         int32_t rowsPerChunk = rows/chunks;
00204 
00205         for (int32_t chunk = 0; chunk < chunks; ++chunk)
00206         {
00207                 int32_t startRow = chunk*rowsPerChunk;
00208                 Uint16Vector values;
00209                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(dataPlane->GetData(0, startRow, rowsPerChunk, values));
00210 
00211                 int32_t rowsInVector = rowsPerChunk;
00212                 if (dataPlane->Rows() < startRow+rowsPerChunk)
00213                         rowsInVector = dataPlane->Rows() - startRow;
00214 
00215                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(values.size() == rowsInVector);
00216 
00217                 // Check the values
00218                 for( int32_t row = startRow; row < rowsInVector+startRow; ++row )
00219                 {
00220                         u_int16_t expected = (u_int16_t)(row*10+row);
00221                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(values[row-startRow] == expected);
00222                 }
